      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GORRINGE (1) is super consistent overall, having placed 10 of 20 career runs. Finished in the minors latest when second (25.74) at Geelong and may be close to breaking through. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Deserves serious consideration. RUPEE MCGRAW (2) is generally an honest type in the frame at 24 of 56 starts but missed the placings last time when fourth (29.79) over 515m at this track. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. SCOUT ACE (4) is looking to continue her winning ways off a handy 25.91 victory in a Grade 5 at Warragul. Top win latest and can measure up again. ILLUMINATOR (7) will be hard to beat despite making his debut at this trip.",
